      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A picture credit with an article on Thursday, about a visit to North Korea by Gov. Bill Richardson of New Mexico to retrieve the remains of six Americans killed in the Korean War, misstated the photographer's surname. The Associated Press picture, showing Governor Richardson and other officials with cases containing the remains, was by Foster Klug, not King.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>A picture credit with an article on Thursday, about a visit to North Korea by Gov. Bill Richardson of New Mexico to retrieve the remains of six Americans killed in the Korean War, misstated the photographer's surname. The Associated Press picture, showing Governor Richardson and other officials with cases containing the remains, was by Foster Klug, not King.</p>
      </block>
